♪I stood there,
shaken and choking on words♪

265
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:11,929
♪I turned away in tears, falling apart♪

266
00:17:11,930 --> 00:17:15,499
♪You turned away
with a smile and goodbye♪

267
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:18,960
♪That moment blurred into a haze♪

268
00:17:19,110 --> 00:17:22,229
♪Leaving only the sea, the sky♪

269
00:17:22,230 --> 00:17:23,739
♪And the sound of me choking back tears♪

270
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:26,619
♪I longed to hold you tighter♪

271
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:30,910
♪But you let go without looking back♪

272
00:17:30,990 --> 00:17:34,159
♪Your fading figure declared it all♪

273
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:39,120
♪And defined the sound of heartbreak♪

